comments: Noel (NYK) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Murray's (SAS) path and does not deliver any contact.
Following the pass, Randle (NYK) and DeRozan (SAS) engage and disengage with each other.
Noel (NYK) makes marginal contact with Poeltl (SAS) as he moves to establish picking position.
Poeltl (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bullock's (NYK) path and does not deliver any contact.
Bullock (NYK) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) makes contact with Burks' (NYK) arm and affects his ability to maintain possession of the ball.
Replay review of the play overturned the on-court out-of-bounds ruling. Barrett (NYK) does not step out of bounds and possession is correctly awarded to NYK.

DeRozan's (SAS) arm makes contact with the ball and dislodges the ball from Randle (NYK). Johnson (SAS) does not make contact with Randle's arm that affects his ability to maintain possession of the ball and the body contact is marginal.
Johnson (SAS) legally contests Randle's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
As Murray (SAS) lowers his shoulder and dribbles into Noel (NYK), Noel makes marginal contact with Murray.
Noel (NYK) absorbs the contact as he and Murray (SAS) meet during Murray's driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) makes marginal contact with Poeltl (SAS) as Noel (NYK) taps the rebound away from Poeltl.
Johnson (SAS) legally contests Burks' (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Walker IV (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bullock's (NYK) path and does not deliver any contact.
Ntilikina (NYK) moves laterally into DeRozan's (SAS) path and the body contact affects his SQBR.
Bullock (NYK) makes contact with Johnson's (SAS) body during his driving shot attempt.
DeRozan (SAS) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
Bullock (NYK) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
DeRozan (SAS) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
